Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,are what have determined the situation.\NOtherwise it looks like an arbitrary god
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,just um didn't give a rap about this kid\Nand favored this one or what? How do you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:19:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,explain God?\NH
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the best uses of kinesiology is\Nas a research tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Within 3 minutes flat, you can satisfy\Nall your questions about karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's if you're slow.\NWithin about one minute flat, you can
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,discover\Nthe likelihoods of why your life is the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,way it is. and certain things have\Nrecurred. And as people get into
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual study, they begin to sort of\Nintuitively get, you know, I must have
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.67,0:19:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,done something in some lifetime to\Nexplain why this is the 14th time a
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,white truck has run into the back of my\Ncar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,14 times, 14 different cities. There's\Ngot to be something there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, we we've all had things\Nrecurrent patterns in our life that are
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond explanation\Nthat you can consult all the wise ones
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.88,0:20:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of the world and frankly they don't know\Nthem. They don't know the answers
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,unless\Nyou're aware of the reality of the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual domain\Nand that it overrules the physical.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.96,0:20:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It overrules the physical.\NIt's only when a you identify a certain
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,pattern and then you say you know it's\Nvery likely that such and such happened
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll find yes it did in fact such\Nand such happened
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,for all this sequence of events that\Nhave happened let's say in relationships
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.03,0:20:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I must have been an so at one in some\Nlifetime
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the only explanation is it why\Nwhy ship. Everybody beat up on you and
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:21:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,give you a hard time in relationships in\Nthis lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they're waiting for you, folks.\NThat's generally
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,uh the truth of it.\NAll right. So, you don't have to be a
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.79,0:21:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,rocket scientist to get what it's all\Nabout. that it seems rather obvious that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.15,0:21:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,every decision\Nthen sets up a vibrational pattern
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.55,0:21:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhere in the soul body\Nwhich exists over time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and thus we see in this lifetime\Nthe externalization the physicality the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,expression of that which we have become\NI always thought Jesus Christ didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,talk too much about karma for a couple\Nof reasons. First of all, it would have
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.12,0:21:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,made him unpopular in the society in\Nwhich he was living.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.20,0:22:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't in India, you know, it wasn't\Nfar east where it would have been so
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.12,0:22:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,what? No, it was cuz such things were\Nknown for thousand years before the
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.24,0:22:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,birth of Christ in the far east. But\Nwhere he grew up, they were pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,rudimentary. The calibrated level of\Nconsciousness at the time of Jesus was
