Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.64,0:23:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,study and teach karma. So I thought he\Njust bypassed it as as unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.36,0:23:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave the folks enough to think about\Nit anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.64,0:24:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A more sophisticated group. I think if\Nhe was speaking to people of a more
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.91,0:24:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,advanced consciousness,\Nthere might have been greater
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.44,0:24:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,explanation.\NAs we've said in previous lectures, the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.44,0:24:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,purpose of uh the life of Jesus Christ\Nwas salvation. That he did come down
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.60,0:24:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,directly from heaven as a manifestation\Ndirectly from heaven and had no prior
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.64,0:24:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,lifetimes,\Nno human lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.60,0:24:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct, is it?\NSo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.48,0:24:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,he wasn't really gung-ho on the subject\Nto begin with. Having
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.52,0:24:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,not had a lot of previous lifetimes,\Nhis familiarities was with heaven and
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.44,0:24:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the nature of heaven and how one gets\Nthere
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.60,0:24:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and how one avoids the other direction.\NThe Buddha on the other hand had many
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.12,0:25:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,many previous lifetimes\Nand therefore spoke freely of it. Let's
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.79,0:25:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,see the Buddha did indeed in fact have\Nmany previous human lifetimes with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.52,0:25:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. So\Ntwo different ways of approaching the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.60,0:25:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,subject.\NIf what your spiritual difficulties are
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.40,0:25:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,now is the real of your karmic\Ninheritance from prior lifetimes, it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.72,0:25:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't really change it. What it does\Ndo is make it more acceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.32,0:25:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If buses keep running into the back of\Nyour car and then you find in some
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.76,0:25:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,lifetime you drove your oxen over your\Nneighbors
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.24,0:25:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,gardens periodically out of paranoia or\Nwhatever. It wouldn't make sense, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.15,0:25:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So,\Na little karmic research into your own
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.00,0:25:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,particular grievances\Ngets rid of self-pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.03,0:25:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,gets rid of self-pity,\Nindignant rage,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.44,0:26:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,resentment.\NHow could God be so unfair?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.44,0:26:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was a kid, all everybody's going\Nout for football. Football. Christ, I
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.44,0:26:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,weighed 62 lbs.\NSo, I used to hang like this every day
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.79,0:26:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,cuz I thought I'd get I could stretch\Nmyself out and get taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.84,0:26:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And I ate a lot, but you I couldn't get\Nfatter or taller. So,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.15,0:26:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,uh you see, it's like unfair, isn't it?\NI mean, the other kids are misorous.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.12,0:26:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They get out there and knock people over\Nand wrestle with each other and all
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.64,0:26:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,kinds of wild things.\NAnd I'm reading a book, so
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.32,0:26:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,karmic propensity then\Nso many people then have many
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.52,0:26:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,resentments about many things in their\Nlife and if you check back on them
