Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.28,0:52:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to take now is stand up and\Ntake us on. You got big trouble. Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.52,0:52:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The best defense is a good offense, huh?\NWell,
