Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.88,0:52:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,look fierce and see if that holds off\Nanybody with any common sense. But megal
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.24,0:52:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,megalomaniacs don't have common sense.\NIf you see a walk across the the line
