Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.92,0:56:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The karmic potentiality of humanness\Nitself
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.28,0:56:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as one's own individual karma.\NOne also shares sort of in ethnic karma
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.83,0:56:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,uh national karma. If you live in a\Ncertain country, you sort of share the
