Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.92,0:56:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have a an infinite number of\Ncomponents
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.72,0:56:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to what one would call one's own\Nindividual karma. It's not individual
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.92,0:56:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but we call it individual. Unique in\Nthat certain patterns peculiar to your
