Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.40,0:57:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Um what I just said is a fact resist.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.40,0:57:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people have lived um most people in\Nthis room have lived many previous
