Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.72,0:57:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,26. So that's just of academic interest.\NUh so if all of us have lived an average
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.28,0:57:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,of 24 lifetimes, some people are greedy\Nand live 50 or 60 and others have only
