Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.07,0:58:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it the last time.\NThe importance of it is you got it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.79,0:58:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The importance is that we have it now.\NHowever, what we're trying to do is
