Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.92,0:58:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the capacities to be hard on yourself is\Nalleviated. In psychoanalysis the first
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.92,0:58:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,rule, you know, I did psychoanalysis and\NI was psycho analyzed.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.64,0:58:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh the first rule in in psychoanalysis\Nwas to approach the patient from the
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.83,0:58:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,side of the super ego. First relieve\Ntheir excessive punitive conscience
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.83,0:58:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,before you start digging up material\Nfrom the unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.35,0:58:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,First get the conscience to be a little\Nbit more reasonable
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.24,0:59:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,before you start looking at\Nulterior motives and things that are
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.07,0:59:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,repressed. The reason they're repressed\Nis because they're so hateful because
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.88,0:59:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,they make you feel so guilty\Nbecause they're so awful that you
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.68,0:59:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't tell anybody on the planet. Now\Nyou're supposed to lay on the couch and
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.88,0:59:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,reveal them to your analyst.\NSo
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.44,0:59:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the analyst aligns himself with the\Nperson's healthy healthy side and tries
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.04,0:59:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to amilarate\Nthe sadistic nature of the super ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.11,0:59:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The conscience tends to be sadistic.\NYou see that expressed in society.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.20,0:59:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want to just capture the bad\Npeople. We want to kill them,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.00,0:59:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,exterminate them, electrocute them, and\Ntorture them a little bit before they
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.24,0:59:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,go.\NYes. And that's what the super ego and
