Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.04,1:00:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That which you would condemn others to\Nis exactly what your unconscious
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.92,1:00:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,condemns you to.\NYou cannot judge savagely out there and
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.76,1:00:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,think that when it comes up within\Nyourself because the super ego will not
